originalText.text:
Nicole is the absolute best personal trainer I have ever worked with. I started training with her promptly after I was cleared by my OB-GYN after giving birth. Nicole’s unique training methodology helped me be back in shape in no time, in an intentional way. When we met for the first session I could not do one push-up even with knees down, and in two months, I was able to do 10, with knees off the floor and great form! She is fun, creative, educated and super informed and makes working out feel enjoyable! I
wouldn’t work with anyone else!

originalText.text: Nicole is a fantastic trainer - you can tell she really thinks about her clients' personal needs and always comes prepared with a customized workout for them. As someone who hates going to the gym, I've found Nicole to be amazing at keeping me engaged and challenged in each session. I came to her looking to get in shape postpartum, and I can see and feel results in just a few months. She's also been really flexible around my schedule and needs juggling childcare and work. I wouldn't hesitate to recommend her to anyone.
